msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: src/content/moneropedia/en/fcmp++.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **anonymity set is the entire set of Monero transactions in history**, not a ring of 16.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: src/content/moneropedia/en/fcmp++.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Double-spend detection** still works using linkable tags that cannot be tied back to a concrete on-chain output.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: src/content/moneropedia/en/fcmp++.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Spend authorization** is cleanly separated: the proof shows the spender controls the key to _some_ valid output in the global set, but never which one.\n"
msgstr ""

